{
  "chapter": 236,
  "chapter_summary": "第236章《尔虞我诈》：徐子陵扮成岳山模样来到荒庙，与石青璇相遇。石青璇以箫音击退邪派高手的魔音侵袭，展现出以音破音的绝技。随后邪门八大高手中的尤鸟倦、金环真、丁九重、周老叹先后现身。金环真与周老叹暗中串谋欺骗尤鸟倦，四人各怀鬼胎、尔虞我诈。石青璇在关键时刻出声喝止众人，展现出超然的气度。徐子陵从中洞察到邪派高手之间的复杂关系，并对石青璇的箫音造诣有了更深的认识。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "请问前辈是那一位高人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "姑娘转过身来一看，不就可知老夫是谁吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "前辈武功虽然高明，却非我等待的人。若只是偶然路过，听得箫音寻来，那晚辈要奉劝前辈立即远离，否则将卷入毫无必要的江湖恩怨里。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "我偏不信邪，要在旁看看。姑娘不用理会老夫的生死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贵客既临，何不入庙一晤，石之轩和碧秀心之女石青璇在此恭候四位前辈法驾。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "text": "适才金宗主已被我箫音所伤，仍要逞强出手，实在太不自量力。走吧！迟恐不及。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "金环真",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "text": "我怎知道？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "speaker_name": "尤鸟倦",
      "listener": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "text": "还以为你这丫头尽得碧秀心的真传，且聪明绝顶，原来只是个蠢丫头，竟不知这世上有一将功成万骨枯的千古至理名言，这淫妇只是派来摸你底细的先头部队，现在你有多少斤两，已尽在本人计算中。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "text": "想不到二十年前名列邪门八大高手之一的倒行逆施尤鸟倦是如此胆小和浅薄之徒，只徒逞口舌之快，却无胆登堂入室，是否顾忌这位偶然路经的前辈呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "金环真",
      "listener": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "text": "尤老大，放心吧！这位老前辈绝非天刀宋缺，不过休想我会为你出手试探。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "speaker_name": "尤鸟倦",
      "listener": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "text": "为甚么不肯？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "金环真",
      "listener": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "text": "老娘怕了他嘛！若惹得两个人夹攻我一个，你又见死不救，那时我岂非自寻死路，老娘才犯不着为你这么做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "text": "尤小鬼终于肯来丢人现眼吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "speaker_name": "尤鸟倦",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "老头子的口气真大，给本人报上名来，看看你是否有资格唤我作小鬼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "text": "老夫成名之时，你还在吃着你娘的奶子。少说废话，老夫今天口馋得很，就把你宰了来吃，出手吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_jiu_chong",
      "speaker_name": "丁九重",
      "listener": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "text": "好笑啊好笑！尤鸟儿不如易名作惊弓之鸟，因为你的小胆儿早在二十年前给宋缺吓破。否则怎会厚颜至此，给人喊打喊杀，仍要把头缩到龟壳内去？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "金环真",
      "listener": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "text": "尤老大你今天是怎么搅的，区区一个丁大帝都收拾不了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "text": "小妹你不是亦毫无长进吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhou_lao_tan",
      "text": "周老叹！你给老夫滚出来，让你的小妹子看看。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_lao_tan",
      "speaker_name": "周老叹",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "唉！你这老头儿究竟是何方神圣？现在连我周老叹都很想知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "金环真",
      "listener": "char_zhou_lao_tan",
      "text": "比那晚的星空更要美哩！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_niao_juan",
      "speaker_name": "尤鸟倦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好淫妇！竟串谋来骗我，厉害！佩服！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_jiu_chong",
      "speaker_name": "丁九重",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "外敌当前，我们是否应先解决敌人，才轮到算自家人的恩怨？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qing_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "石青璇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慢着！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 236,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    }
  ],
